Uses VS Code, one main file main.py, easy to run with python main.py.

Personal user profile that drives budget recommendations.

Budgeting lesson plus interactive budget game.

Investment game with three stocks and:

Random daily price moves.

Text charts in the terminal that look animated as days progress.

Real matplotlib line charts that pop up in a separate window.

Hint Bot you can ask about budgets, investing, or debt.

Interest calculators for:

Simple savings.

IRA, 401k, 403b style retirement accounts.

Savings accounts.

Housing loan (mortgage) payment and interest, with an optional amortization chart.

All calculators and simulations are clearly labeled as educational, not real financial advice.
